Class DummyTextRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • preibisch_imagej.render.DummyTextRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TextRenderer

    public class DummyTextRenderer
extends Object
implements TextRenderer
    A dummy implementation of the TextRenderer interface. Necessary to allow any UI that does not support text rendering to still initialize correctly.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
